         <div type="translation">
            <ab>MH 2625, recto: (1) In the name of the Father and the (2) Son and the Holy Ghost, (3) on this day, which is the eighth day (4) of Tobe, I, Toulit, (5) daughter of John, in (6) ...write to you, (7) Maria, wife of Dioskoros, (8) saying: Seeing that I asked (9) your husband, and you gave half a (10) tremis in loaves to me for my pressing need, now, (12) by the will of God, I am prepared (13) to pay it (14) to you in the coming Paone (15) without any dispute.  (16) For your assurance, then, I have (17) drawn up this undertaking (18) for you, which is confirmed...</ab>
